---
Source:
  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  ID: 50ae0a98-5702-40cb-8c11-4c6297aa457a
  Translator: Burton Watson
By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 12
  Paragraph: 62
Title: Heaven And Earth
---
When the leper woman gives birth to a child in the dead of the night,
she rushes to fetch a torch and examine it, trembling with terror lest
it look like herself.
